branchItem.description:
&lt;p&gt;
The HRSE recirculating chiller is a basic version of HRS featuring air cooled refrigerant and omitting the heating function. Three cooling capacities are available. The operator interface includes an easy-fill fluid tank with level check, intuitive keypad and digital display, and tool free filter removal. This model is compatible with single phase 100 VAC 50/60Hz power.
&lt;/p&gt;

